        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>2012 SST correction</para>
<para>Jaeglé, L., Quinn, P. K., Bates, T. S., Alexander, B., and Lin, J.-T.: Global distribution of sea salt aerosols: new constraints from in situ and remote sensing observations, Atmos. Chem. Phys., 11, 3137–3157, <ulink url="https://doi.org/10.5194/acp-11-3137-2011">https://doi.org/10.5194/acp-11-3137-2011</ulink>, 2011.</para>
