      <memberdef kind="function" id="group__catchem__seasalt__process_1gafc8b2b984c59ea821ef30355745b6160" prot="private" static="no" const="no" explicit="no" inline="no" virt="non-virtual">
        <type>subroutine</type>
        <definition>subroutine seasaltscheme_gong03_mod::weibulldistribution</definition>
        <argsstring>(gweibull, weibullflag, wm, rc)</argsstring>
        <name>weibulldistribution</name>
        <qualifiedname>seasaltscheme_gong03_mod::weibulldistribution</qualifiedname>
        <param>
          <type>real(fp), intent(inout)</type>
          <defname>gweibull</defname>
        </param>
        <param>
          <type>logical, intent(in)</type>
          <defname>weibullflag</defname>
        </param>
        <param>
          <type>real(fp), intent(in)</type>
          <defname>wm</defname>
        </param>
        <param>
          <type>integer, intent(out)</type>
          <defname>rc</defname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Calculate the weibull distribution for 10m wind speed (u10, v10) </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>The Weibull distribution correction ends up being a multiplicative constant (g) times our present source function (see Eq. 12 in Fan &amp; Toon, 2011 and notes for (9/22/11). This constant is derived from the incomplete and complete forms of the gamma function, hence the utilities pasted below. The Weibull function and shape parameters (k, c) assumed are from Justus 1978.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="inout">gweibull</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Multiplicative constant </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">weibullFlag</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Flag for weibull correction </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">wm</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>10m wind speed </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="out">RC</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Return Code</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<blockquote><para><zwj/> </para>
</blockquote></para>
        </detaileddescription>
